[
    {
        "source_sentence": "合部金光明經卷第三",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隋大興善寺沙門釋寶貴合",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "梁三藏真諦譯",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "陀羅尼最淨地品第六",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，師子相無礙光焰菩薩與無量億眾從座俱起，偏袒右肩，右膝著地，合掌恭敬頂禮佛足，以種種華香、寶幢、幡蓋以為供養，而作是言：「以幾因緣得菩提心？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者是菩提心？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於菩提者，現在心不可得、未來心不可得、過去心不可得；離菩提者，菩提心亦不可得。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提者，不可言說；心者，亦無色、無相，無事、無業、非可造作；眾生者，亦不可得、亦不可知。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何諸法甚深之義而可得知？」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提，祕密事業造作，不可得知；離菩提，菩提心亦不可得。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提者不可言說，心亦無相，眾生亦不可得知。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如意，心亦如是；如心，菩提亦如是；如心、如菩提，眾生亦如是；如眾生，一切三世法亦如是。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，菩薩摩訶薩得名是心通一切法，是說菩提菩提心。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提，非過去、非未來、非現在；心亦如是、眾生亦如是，於如此中亦不可得。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切法無生故，菩提不可得、菩提名不可得，眾生、眾生名不可得，聲聞、聲聞名不可得，緣覺、緣覺名不可得，菩薩、菩薩名不可得，佛、佛名不可得，行非行不可得、行非行名不可得。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於一切寂靜法中而得安住、依一切功德善根而得發出，是名初發菩提心。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0372c28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「譬如寶須彌山王，是名檀波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「第二發心，譬如大地持一一法事故，是名尸波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如師子臆長毫獸王有大神力，獨步無畏，無有戰怖。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第三心說羼提波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如風輪，那羅延力勇壯速疾。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第四心不退轉，是名毘梨耶波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如七寶樓觀有四階道，清涼之風來吹四門。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第五心上種種功德法藏猶未滿足，是名禪波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如日輪，光耀炎盛。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第六心能破滅生死大闇故，是名般若波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大富商主能令一切心願滿足。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第七心能令得度生死險惡道故、能令得多功德寶故，是名方便勝智波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如月淨圓滿。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第八心一切境界清淨具足故，是名願波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如轉輪聖王，主兵、寶臣如意處分。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第九心善能莊嚴清淨佛土，功德普洽，廣利一切故，是名力波羅蜜因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如虛空及轉輪聖王。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，第十心於一切境界皆悉通達故、於一切法自在至灌頂位故，是名智波羅蜜因。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，十種菩薩摩訶薩菩提心因。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依五種法成就菩薩摩訶薩檀波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、信根，二者、慈悲，三者、無求欲心，四者、攝受一切眾生，五者、願求一切智智。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是，善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依是五法檀波羅蜜能得成就。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依是五法菩薩摩訶薩成就尸波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、三業清淨，二者、不為一切眾生作煩惱因緣，三者、斷諸惡道、開善道門，四者、過於聲聞、緣覺之地，五者、一切功德願滿足故。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373a27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依是五法尸波羅蜜能得成就。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，依五法菩薩摩訶薩成就羼提波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、伏貪、瞋煩惱，二者、不惜身命、不生安樂止息之觀，三者、思惟往業，四者、為欲成熟一切眾生功德善根發慈悲心，五者、為得甚深無生法忍。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就羼提波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，依五法菩薩摩訶薩成就毘梨耶波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、與諸煩惱不得共住，二者、福德未具不得安樂，三者、一切難行不生厭心，四者、為欲利益一切眾生成就大慈悲攝受，五者、願求不退轉地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就毘梨耶波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，依五法成就菩薩摩訶薩禪那波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、一切善法攝持不散；二者、解脫生死，二處不著；三者、願得神通，為成就眾生善根故；四者、發心洗浣法界，為清淨心故；五者、為斷眾生一切煩惱根故。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就禪那波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，有五法菩薩摩訶薩成就般若波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、一切諸佛、菩薩聰慧大智供養親近，心無厭足；二者、諸佛如來說甚深法，心常樂聞，無有厭足；三者、真俗勝智；四者、見思煩惱如是勝智能分別斷；五者、於世間五明之法皆悉通達。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就般若波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，依五法菩薩摩訶薩成就方便勝智波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、於一切眾生意欲、煩惱、行心悉通達；二者、無量對治諸法之門心皆曉了；三者、大慈大悲，入出自在；四者、於摩訶波羅蜜多能修行，成熟滿足，悉皆願求；五者、一切佛法了達攝受，皆悉願求。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就方便勝智波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有五法菩薩摩訶薩成就願波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、於一切法本來不生、不滅，不有、不無，心安樂住；二者、觀一切諸法最妙、一切垢清淨，心得安住；三者、過一切相，心如如，無作、無行，不異、不動，安心於如；四者、為利益眾生事於俗諦中得安心住；五者、於奢摩他毘鉢舍那同時能住。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就願波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依此五法菩薩摩訶薩成就力波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、一切眾生心行險惡智力能解；二者、能令一切眾生入於甚深之法；三者、一切眾生往還生死，隨其因緣如是見知；四者、於一切眾生三聚智力能分別知；五者、如理為種、為熟、為脫，如是說法皆是智力故。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就力波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有五法菩薩摩訶薩修行成就智波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、於一切法分別善惡具足智能，二者、於黑白法遠離攝受具足智能，三者、於生死涅槃不厭不喜具足智能，四者、大福德行、大智慧行得度究竟具足智能，五者、一切諸佛不共法等及一切智智具足灌頂智能。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名菩薩摩訶薩成就智波羅蜜。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何者波羅蜜義？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0373c29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行道勝利是波羅蜜義；大甚深智滿足是波羅蜜義；行、非行法，心不執著，是波羅蜜義；生死過失、涅槃功德，正覺、正觀，是波羅蜜義；愚人、智人皆悉攝受，是波羅蜜義；能現種種珍妙法寶，是波羅蜜義；無礙解脫智滿足，是波羅蜜義；法界、眾生界正分別知，是波羅蜜義；檀等及智能令至不退轉地，是波羅蜜義；能令滿足無生法忍，是波羅蜜義；一切眾生功德善根能令成熟，是波羅蜜義；於菩提清涼道場佛慧十力、四無畏、不共法等成就，是波羅蜜義；生死、涅槃皆是妄見，能度無餘，是波羅蜜義；濟度一切，是波羅蜜義；一切外人來相詰難，善能解釋令其降伏，是波羅蜜義；能轉十二行法輪，是波羅蜜義；無所著、無所見，無患累、無異思惟，是波羅蜜義。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初菩薩地是相前現：三千大千世界無量無邊種種寶物等藏皆悉盈滿。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩二地是相前現：三千大千世界地平如掌，無量無數種種妙色清淨之寶、莊嚴之具。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩三地是相前現：自身勇健，鎧仗莊嚴，一切怨賊皆能摧伏。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩四地是相前現：四方風輪、種種妙華悉皆散灑圓滿地上。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩五地是相前現：如寶女人一切莊嚴，其身頂上散多那華，妙寶、瓔珞貫飾身首。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩六地是相前現：七寶華池有四階道，金沙遍滿，清淨無穢，八功德水皆悉盈滿，欝波羅花、拘物頭華、分陀利華莊嚴其池，於華池所自身遊戲，快樂清淨，清涼無比。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩七地是相前現：左邊、右邊應墮地獄，以菩薩力故，還得不墮，無有損傷、無有痛惱。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩八地是相前現：左邊、右邊，師子臆長毫獸王，一切眾獸悉皆怖畏。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩九地是相前現：轉輪聖王無量億眾圍遶供養，頂上白蓋——無量眾寶之所莊嚴——以覆於上。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩十地是相前現：如來之身金色晃耀，無量淨光悉皆圓滿，無量億梵王圍遶恭敬供養，轉於無上微妙法輪。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩悉見。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何初地而名歡喜？",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得出世心，昔所未得而今始得，大事大用，如意所願悉皆成就，大歡喜慶樂故，是故初地名為歡喜地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一切微細之罪、破戒過失皆清淨故，是故二地說名無垢地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「無量智慧光明三昧不可傾動、無能摧伏，聞持陀羅尼為作本故，是故三地說名明地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「能燒煩惱，以智慧火增長光明，是修行道品依處所故，是故四地說名焰地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是修行方便勝智自在難得故、見思煩惱不可伏故，是故五地說名難勝地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「行法相續，了了顯現，無相、多思惟現前故，是故六地說名現前地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「無漏、無間、無相思惟解脫三昧，遠修行故，是地清淨，無障、無礙，是故七地說名遠行地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「無相、正思惟修得自在，諸煩惱行不能令動，是故八地說名不動地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「說一切種種法而得自在，無患累故、增長智慧自在無礙故，是故九地說名善慧地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「法身如虛空、智慧如大雲，能令遍滿覆一切故，是故第十名法雲地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「初地欲行有相道是無明障礙、生死怖畏是無明，依二種麁心是初地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「微細罪過因無明、種種業行相因無明，依二種麁心是二地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「昔所未得勝利，得故動涌，因無明；不具聞持陀羅尼，因無明。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是三地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「味禪定樂生愛著心，因無明；微妙淨法愛，因無明。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是四地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一意欲入涅槃思惟、一意欲入生死思惟。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是涅槃思惟、是生死思惟，無明為因；生死涅槃不平等思惟，無明為因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是五地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「行法相續，了了顯現，無明為因；法相數數，行至於心，無明為因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是六地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「微細諸相，或現、不現，無明；一味熟思惟欲斷未得方便，無明。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是七地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於無相法多用功力，無明；執相自在，難可得度，無明。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是八地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「說法無量、名味句無量、智慧分別無量，未能攝持，無明；四無礙辯未得自在，無明。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是九地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「最大神通未得如意，無明；微妙祕密之藏修行未足，無明。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依二種麁心是十地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一切境界微細智礙，無明為因；未來是礙不更生，未得不更生智，無明為因。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0374c29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是如來地障。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是，善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於初菩薩地行向檀波羅蜜、於二地行向尸波羅蜜、於三地行向羼提波羅蜜、四地行向毘梨耶波羅蜜、五地行向禪那波羅蜜、六地行向般若波羅蜜、七地行向方便勝智波羅蜜、八地行向願波羅蜜、九地行向力波羅蜜、十地行向智波羅蜜。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩初發心名妙寶起三摩提攝受得生、第二發心可愛住三摩提攝受得生、第三發心難動三摩提攝受得生、第四發心不退轉三昧攝受得生、第五發心寶華三昧攝受得生、第六發心日圓光焰三昧攝受得生、第七發心一切願如意成就三昧攝受得生、第八發心現在佛現前證住三昧攝受得生、第九發心智藏三昧攝受得生、第十發心首楞嚴摩伽三昧攝受得生。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名諸菩薩摩訶薩十種發心。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩於此初地，依功德力名陀羅尼得生。」",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊而說呪曰：「◎怛姪他(天可切，後九篇初他字悉同此音)(其一)富樓尼(念履切，後九篇音尼字悉同此音)(其二)那羅弟(吳音呼弟)(其三)頭吼頭吼頭吼(其四)那(移我切)跋修履愈(其五)烏婆娑底(知履切)(其六)那(移我切)跋旃杜魯(其七)弟(吳音呼弟)愈多底(吳音呼底)(其八)多跋鐸洛衫(霜艦切)(其九)但地(圖賣切)波履訶嵐(里含切)(其十)苟留(良吼切)(其十一)鎖訶(虎可切，後九篇末訶字悉同此音)(其十二)「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是陀羅尼名過一恒河沙數諸佛為救護。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初地菩薩誦持此陀羅尼呪，得度脫一切怖畏、一切惡獸、一切惡鬼，人非人等災橫、諸惱，解脫五障，不忘念初地。",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375b06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0664_003:0375b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
